  "title": "Admin Officer [Shipping & Operations]/ 5days/ Up to $3K Basic+AWS+Bonus/ Central",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Up to $3,000 basic + AWS + Bonus + Benefits. </strong></li><li><strong>Permanent role/ Hybrid office/ 5 workdays/ Central area.</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Our client, a reputable and leading marine transportation company providing a wide variety of liquid bulk\ncargoes services to their clients. </strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct compliance checks in accordance with Japan\nand Singapore FDA requirements</li><li>Manage and maintain owner accounts</li><li>Handle accounts payable processes, including\npurchase invoices, FDA records, payments, and receipts in Sage</li><li>Issue invoices and monitor shipping schedules to\nensure timely billing</li><li>Work closely with the operations team to support\nday-to-day activities</li><li>Assist with the preparation of reports,\nregulatory filings, and related documentation</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Accounting or equivalent.</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information:</strong></p><p><strong>To apply please click on the APPLY NOW to\nsubmit your resume with the following details:</strong></p><ul><li>Reason for leaving each past & current\nemployment</li><li>Salary drawn for each past & current\nemployment</li><li>Expected Salary</li></ul><ul><li>Earliest availability date</li></ul><p><strong>We regret only shortlisted candidates\nwill be notified. </strong></p><p><strong>Lionel Cheow</strong></p><p><strong>EA License | 14C7092</strong></p><p><strong>EA Registration Number | R1105005</strong></p>",
